title: Part 1: AFC/NFC Over/Unders With Cousin Sal
description:
Football is back! In Part 1 of a two-part Sunday podcast, The Ringer’s Bill Simmons is joined by Cousin Sal to run through expected win totals of every NFL team and make their over/under picks.

Host: Bill Simmons
Guest: Cousin Sal
Producer: Kyle Crichton
